| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7895 — Recovery Inhibition (medusa)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c9748141-41fb-5263-9cae-12f7b461e543"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
